Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:06.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind. Open your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:23.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Far beyond the deep blue Earth,\nyou and I shall meet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:24.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a gentle breeze goes by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:28.51,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.51,0:00:29.98,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:37.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A snow-white feather will come\nfluttering down, swaying gently in the air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.11,0:00:44.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without holding back, I want to\nenvelope you, my one and only love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.22,0:00:53.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I have the power to protect\nthe one I love, right here in my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:01:00.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind.\NJust as I've always dreamed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:07.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let the wind carry off\nyour hopes, faraway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:14.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have wings nobody can see.\NLook, you have them, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:22.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll take us to where we can be free.\NAnyone can be free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.36,0:01:26.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky is so blue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:36.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss... I think you've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.21,0:01:38.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:41.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time to lecture your customer,\nwhy don't you just hit me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:45.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Vodka, Sprodka! I'll take it straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:54.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that girl showed up, I've been\nstripped of my title as campus queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.43,0:01:58.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forced to spend my nights\ndrowning my sorrows alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.06,0:02:01.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why, oh why did this have to happen to\nme?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:03.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everything that's happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:06.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...it's all Belldandy's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:11.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, miss... are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:20.81,AMG episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah! Choosing Between\nthe Goddess and the Queen?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:28.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, my head hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:32.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I must've had too much\nto drink last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:38.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to me while I slept?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:40.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just hold on a minute!{\i0}\NWhat did you do to me while I slept?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:43.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You passed out, and I'm the one\nwho brought you home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:46.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You got me falling-down drunk and\ndid this and that to me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:49.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea! I'm a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.38,0:02:51.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! I'm not into\nthat kind of thing, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:55.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you... Belldandy's a\nthorn in your side, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:57.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:58.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You heard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:03.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just sign a contract with me, and\nI'll help you banish Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:06.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...so you can regain your title\nas campus queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:10.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:14.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So what are we going to do with this\nnow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:16.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can bet Marller will be back for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:19.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You mean that demon's still around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:23.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because this CD is\na hindrance to Marller...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:25.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A hindrance to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}\NA hindrance to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:32.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But as long as it's in our hands,\nit won't be easy for her to make a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:35.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we just seal her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:36.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:39.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that demon,\nI got turned into a scooter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:44.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I was forced to drink a weird potion\nand then I ran all over the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:48.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who made you drink the\npotion, and rode you all over the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:50.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I didn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:53.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But if I didn't get turned back,\nit would've been such a drag.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:57.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind being a motorcycle,\nbut not a scooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:03:59.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let her do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:05.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I have to go head-to-head with\NMarller, I'm going to protect you, Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:11.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But if we do seal her, Marller will have\nto wander through the Dark Realm again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:15.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not go that far,\nif it's at all possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:19.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then\nI'll hold onto this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:23.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just worry about Keiichi,\nand nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:28.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Marller doesn't want to be\nsent back to a place like that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:30.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:34.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we've settled things,\nwhy don't you two go for a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:38.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Brooding over things in the house\nwon't get you anywhere, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:39.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:42.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty, have a good time now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:44.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really! I don't believe Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:47.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we might as well go out,\ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:49.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:04:58.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There they go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:05:02.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even so... that Marller...\ncan I really trust her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:10.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. If you grant my wish,\nI'll help you to banish Belldandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:12.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Help, did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:17.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. So what is this wish of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:21.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you have money in mind,\nI'll pay you whatever you ask for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:22.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have no use for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:25.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't tell me you want to sleep with me!{\i0}\nI have no use for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:28.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm a woman! Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:30.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is it that you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:33.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite simple, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:38.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At least, that's what\nshe said at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:41.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But even if this ends in failure,\nit won't really affect me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:45.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...whereas if I succeed,\nI'll reap all the benefits!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:47.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now's your chance! Finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:51.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!\NJust when we got to the juicy part!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:53.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:56.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:05.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know... this is really awkward!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:08.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:11.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:14.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you came to see Belldandy,\nshe went out with Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:20.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not terribly important, but\nI think I'll wait until she comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:24.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you came here to try to\nsniff out our dark secrets again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:28.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, secrets?\NOf course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:32.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're really a piece of work, going\nto all this trouble to be campus queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:38.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but didn't you enter the\ncontest to vie for the title yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:41.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You two looked so desperate\nto own that title...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:44.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...so I graciously yielded\nmy crown to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:47.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry you didn't realize that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:51.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you to talk, when you're\nthe one who lost to Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:55.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, wasn't it you\nwho lost to Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:59.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids aren't old enough to\nappreciate a mature woman's splendor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:02.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess your breast size\nwas just right for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:07.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What does that have to do with it?\NMy breasts aren't small, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:11.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you dressed yourself in layers\nbecause you were insecure about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:16.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep wearing those revealing\ndresses, you'll only damage your skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:19.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But that's better than\nnot turning any heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:22.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're just an exhibitionist, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:24.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Flat-chested!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:26.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Flasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:35.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, why don't we turn on the TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:39.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good idea. There's a show\nI want to watch now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:41.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let me turn it on for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh? Well, thanks.{\i0}\NWell, let me turn it on for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.47,0:07:46.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Channel 6! Channel 6!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:52.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}KING OF ENKA\N2-hour special{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:58.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:01.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:05.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking this CD with me, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:07.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:11.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're in league\nwith that demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:16.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good night...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:28.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:31.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Is this all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:34.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you came up big for me, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:35.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:39.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am most grateful to you\nfor granting my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:44.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it's my turn. You've got\nto hold up your end of the bargain now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:47.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've already started the wheels turning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:50.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:54.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Balance Sphere\nfor Keiichi Morisato's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:55.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:59.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\NThe human heart is a fragile thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.25,0:09:04.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Once thrown off balance, he won't hear\nthe goddess's voice anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:07.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on! Don't tell me\nyou're a goddess, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:10.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No... a devil. That's what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:15.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't matter to me\nwhat you are as long as...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:18.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...you get rid of Belldandy for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:24.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we have a contract.\NPut your hand on this Balance Sphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:35.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now Keiichi's heart is mired in my spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:41.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more push, and his heart will be\ntipped towards you, just as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:45.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I wish?\nI have no feeling for Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:50.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But if the end result is that\NBelldandy disappears, what do you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:53.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is just a means to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:54.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But of course he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:59.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only using Keiichi Morisato to\nbanish Belldandy once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:03.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now all you have to do is\nmeet up with those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:07.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But that's easier said than done!\NWhere in the world are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:12.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have no fear. The wheels of Fate\nhave already begun to turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:16.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is inevitable now that\nyou will encounter them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:24.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, it sure feels good to be outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:26.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad that we decided to go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:27.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Me, too.{\i0}\nI'm so glad that we decided to go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:31.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:35.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:38.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking that\nit's been a long time since...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:42.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...we spent any quality time\ntogether like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:44.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:47.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, not since Urd came to stay with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:50.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right, things were\npretty hectic for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:54.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's why I'm so\ngrateful to you, Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:56.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Grateful?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:11:00.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for\ntaking a walk with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:04.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really! What's up with her, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:06.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Talking about Fate and all that stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:10.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No way am I going to be able\nto find those two so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:14.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, what am I\nsupposed to do once I find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:17.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She left out all the important details!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:21.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then, since it's still early\nin the day, let's go have a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:23.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:25.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:28.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:41.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is up to you, Sayoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:54.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I really did run into them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:59.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! What a coincidence,\nrunning into each other like this here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:03.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it certainly is a coincidence.\NWhat are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:08.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take a walk\naround the city with Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:13.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see how this is\ngoing to be of any help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:19.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a nice day. We haven't gone out\nin so long, so as a change of pace...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:21.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:26.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In your heart you only have eyes for\nthe woman standing right in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:30.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, Keiichi?\NDo you have a fever or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.63,0:12:33.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:35.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not feeling well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:36.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'd better go home right away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:38.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'd better go home right away.{\i0}\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:39.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can go for a walk some other time.{\i0}\NEverything's just as it always is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:41.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can go for a walk some other time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:44.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you. I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:51.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, if you'd like,\nwhy don't you come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:55.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you two are on a date, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:12:58.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do anything lame\nlike get in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:13:03.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us can hang out\ntogether, right, Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:04.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:08.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We were just thinking of where\nwe could go have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:11.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you have a place in mind,\nwould you take us there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:17.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what's come over you,\nbut I'll keep you company.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:20.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's up with Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:32.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?\NHaven't you ever been to a club before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:35.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't usually\ncome to places like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:40.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm amazed you even\nhad the nerve to ask me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:45.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, that's it, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:47.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth have you\nbeen doing for fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:50.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it is, it's not going\nto get you a lot of dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:51.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:53.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll dance, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:14:01.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going to challenge me on this\ndance floor? I won't lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:20.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could you teach me how to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:23.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I could dance like you,\nI bet I'd have a lot more fun here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:27.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you have talent,\nI'd be happy to show you some moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:31.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?\NYou don't look too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:35.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... I'm fine, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:40.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe you're not having a\ngood time hanging out with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:44.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hang out with Sayoko a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:47.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go on home\nand get some rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:53.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! Mission accomplished!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:57.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The goddess's love can\nno longer reach that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.01,0:14:59.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:04.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you want, Keiichi,\nI'll go home now and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:06.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:10.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:15.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:27.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can it be that you no longer need me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:31.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Victory is mine now!\NThe goddesses will soon be gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:35.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And the demons will reign\nwith this Earth as our fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:38.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}KING OF ENKA 2-hour special\NTHE END{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:45.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next, here is the latest news.\NThis morning in Nekomi Prefecture...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:50.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How dare she subject me to enka...\nthat woman is the devil incarnate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:56.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If she took that CD, that means\NMarller must be behind all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:58.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to be a pain in the... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:00.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:04.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? You don't look happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:06.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking what a great time we had.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:08.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had a good time, too.{\i0}\nI was thinking what a great time we had.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:12.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wish she wasn't scared off so easily... I\nwas hoping for more competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:17.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I ever actually considered\nher to be a true rival, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:19.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:22.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:24.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready to order?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.70,0:16:27.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, what should I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:29.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Two Darjeeling teas, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't told you what I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:35.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. But listen, it's good,\nso just give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:39.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Bring us two of those, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:41.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:45.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You were thinking about\NBelldandy just now, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:47.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:49.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:53.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one I want to\nbe with right now, Sayoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:57.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not true.\nIt's not you who I want to be with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:02.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here is your tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:13.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You know what... this really isn't for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:17.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Belldandy said she liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:20.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's her favorite kind of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:24.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you bringing her up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:27.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You just told me that\nyou wanted to be with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:31.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe how insensitive you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:32.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:36.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:39.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:43.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Telling me you were having a good time\nwith me... you're full of sweet talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:46.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But at the end of the day,\nyou only have Belldandy on your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:48.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:51.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you to dinner\nto make it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:54.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you taking me to a restaurant\nthat meets my standards?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:58.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy's such a terrific cook,\nso let's go to my place for dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:01.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to insult me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:03.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's go look at the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:07.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You said you loved to listen to\nthe sound of the wind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:09.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:15.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A beach with a beautiful view of\nthe sunset... that's what I like!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:19.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember ever saying that\nI liked listening to the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:21.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sayoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:25.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to lie to me,\nthen do me a favor and lie all the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:27.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:31.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For god's sake! I'll never know\nwhat Belldandy sees in this moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:34.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:38.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... Belldandy's the one I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:42.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Belldandy for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:47.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that she's the only one who can\nhandle going out with a moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:58.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm rid of Belldandy,\nit's not going to make me any happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:03.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a fool! Throwing away\nsuch a golden opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:06.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However! I have the CD in my\npossession.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:09.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have this,\nthose goddesses are nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:11.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Marller! Are you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:12.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Urd!{\i0}\NHi, Marller! Are you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:12.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Urd!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:16.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find you, so you'd better brace\nyourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:21.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit of Electricity, Spirit of the Radio\NWaves, Spirit of Television...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:25.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Heed my call and meld all minds into one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.61,0:19:28.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Channel... Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:31.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:33.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:38.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, it's Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:43.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:47.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No... damn that Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:51.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Taking advantage of the fact that I can't\nstop dancing when I hear rock music!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:53.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:58.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but aren't you the devil here?\NNow that I've recovered this thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:14.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No good, she's not home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:17.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is she out somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:20.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now where would Belldandy go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:30.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:35.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If Keiichi no longer wishes to have me\nby his side, then I have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:39.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but to return to Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:42.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:47.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was staying here to\nfulfill my job as a goddess, but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:51.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:54.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:21:00.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:03.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:06.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:13.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know I'd be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:16.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,''Where the wind crossing the vast\nocean...''
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:19.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,''...meets the wind that has\ndescended from the mountains.''
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:22.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You said it was your favorite\nplace to be, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.83,0:21:27.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I was such a jerk\nto you before, but I was wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.53,0:21:31.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I only want to be with one person...\nand that's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:32.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:35.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So please, don't ever leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:38.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stay by my side forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:44.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then you mean it's all right\nto stay by your side, Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.48,0:21:48.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right to fulfill\nour contract, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:51.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The contract has\nnothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.19,0:21:54.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about\ngoddesses or contracts...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:58.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All I want... is for you to stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:22:00.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:14.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do I care about that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.71,0:22:19.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Someday I'm going to defeat Belldandy\nwithout help from anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.64,0:22:22.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And when I do, I'll win him over, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.73,0:22:38.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day when I woke up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.14,0:22:49.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A day like any other...\nanother one just beginning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:59.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There you are, yawning...\nyour face is still so sleepy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.32,0:23:06.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because each peaceful day\nwe share is a miracle to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:12.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is where my heart\nwill always return...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:15.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forever...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.46,0:23:21.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's only one thing I wish for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.38,0:23:27.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I chase after the same dream,\nwherever it may go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.82,0:23:33.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The love I feel for you\ngives me strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:40.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May tomorrow be as joyful as today...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.06,0:23:44.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's my wish...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.41,0:24:00.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was not only joy that the goddess\nbestowed upon this earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.72,0:24:04.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who has emerged from the distortion\nin time along with these system bugs?
